OL,3,C'Tuberculosis outbreak' reported at
OL,4,CCoventry Amazon warehouse
OL,6,FMultiple tuberculosis cases have been
OL,7,Freported at the Amazon fulfilment
OL,8,Fcentre in Coventry, according to the
OL,9,FGMB union.
OL,11,FThe union claims NHS staff attended
OL,12,Fthis week to perform blood tests on
OL,13,Fmembers of staff and is calling on
OL,14,FAmazon to close the site.
OL,16,FThey also want workers to be medically
OL,17,Fsuspended on full pay until
OL,18,F"appropriate infection control
OL,19,Fmeasures are implemented to prevent
OL,20,Ffurther spread of TB".
