OL,6,F"Immediate and decisive action"
OL,8,FGMB Senior Organiser Amanda Gearing
OL,9,Fsaid:
OL,11,F"Currently, Amazon is putting all
OL,12,Fworkers, site visitors, and the local
OL,13,Fand wider communities at risk of
OL,14,Fexposure to a serious infectious
OL,15,Fdisease.
OL,17,F"Coventry Amazon risks becoming the
OL,18,Fengine room of a mass TB outbreak of a
OL,19,Fscale not seen for decades.
