OL,6,F"Immediate and decisive action `
OL,7,Fincluding the temporary closure of
OL,8,FAmazon Coventry - is required to
OL,9,Fprevent this."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Amazon said:
OL,13,F"Nothing is more important than the
OL,14,Fsafety and wellbeing of our team
OL,15,Fmembers. Last year, ten people who
OL,16,Fwork at our Coventry fulfilment centre
OL,17,Ftested positive for non-contagious TB.
