OL,6,F"In line with best practice safety
OL,7,Fprocedures, we immediately followed
OL,8,Fguidance from the NHS and UK Health
OL,9,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) and made all
OL,10,Fpotentially affected employees aware
OL,11,Fof the situation.
OL,13,F"Out of an abundance of caution, we
OL,14,Fare currently running an expanded
OL,15,Fscreening programme with the NHS. To
OL,16,Fdate, no additional cases have been
OL,17,Fidentified, and our site continues to
OL,18,Frun as normal.
