OL,6,F"We will continue to follow guidance
OL,7,Ffrom the experts in the NHS, and would
OL,8,Frespectfully remind public
OL,9,Forganizations of the need for
OL,10,Fresponsible communications where
OL,11,Fmatters of public wellbeing are
OL,12,Fconcerned.'
OL,14,FWhat is tuberculosis?
OL,16,FTuberculosis, or TB, is the world's
OL,17,Fdeadliest infectious disease and kills
OL,18,Fmore than one million people each
OL,19,Fyear, according to World Health
OL,20,FOrganisation data.
